<HL>
   House Unit Votes to Subpoena Milken,
   Offer Immunity in Return for Testimony
   ----
   By Kevin G. Salwen
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
05/02/90
</DATE>
